.SH NAME
rtrs_srv_resp_rdma \- Finish an RDMA request
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "bool" rtrs_srv_resp_rdma
.BI "(struct rtrs_srv_op *id "  ","
.BI "int status "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "id" 12
Internal RTRS operation identifier
.IP "status" 12
Response Code sent to the other side for this operation.
0 = success, <=0 error
.SH "CONTEXT"
any
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Finish a RDMA operation. A message is sent to the client and the
corresponding memory areas will be released.
